r%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-wmykBdQiZlhullR0PPvO_Q">Trần Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/%E1%BB%A8c-nh%C5%A9-m%E1%BA%ABu-k%C3%BD-d%E1%BB%AF-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-ni%C3%AAn-Th%C3%A1i-b%E1%BB%99c-T%C3%B4n-%C4%90%C3%A0i/poem-ecHVX2DUgQwBrupX9xYcxA">Ức nhũ mẫu, ký dữ đồng niên Thái bộc Tôn Đài - 憶乳母，寄與同年太僕尊台</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/author-pEICBCCrXfpItm0RL1cOfw">Đinh Nho Hoàn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Cao/%E1%BB%A8ng-Minh-tr%C3%AC-d%E1%BB%8B-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-u2de-DTEkjKdBJvaJaTEvQ">Ứng Minh trì dị sự - 應明池異事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Cao/author-TGk1BPyzePqXA-ek-telmQ">Vũ Cao</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-giang-th%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-LFVbGDrCcrq1hCo8-XrWqg">Xuân nhật giang thôn kỳ 5 - 春日江村其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
